## üß™ Section 15: Testing Strategy Updates

### New Testing Areas

**Plugin Testing:**
- [ ] Plugin installs correctly from marketplace
- [ ] All components (skills, agents, commands) load
- [ ] Version updates work smoothly
- [ ] Team auto-install works in shared repos
- [ ] Plugin uninstall is clean (no leftovers)

**Subagent Testing:**
- [ ] Enhancer agent invokes correctly
- [ ] Context separation works (main thread stays clean)
- [ ] Enhanced prompts score higher than originals
- [ ] Resumable sessions work (can continue later)
- [ ] Researcher agent finds prompts accurately
- [ ] Search results are relevant and ranked

**CLI Tool Testing:**
- [ ] `npx promptforge@latest` works without installation
- [ ] `--install` flag sets up plugin correctly
- [ ] `--update` flag detects new versions
- [ ] `--browse` shows interactive menu
- [ ] `--stats` displays accurate analytics
- [ ] Works on Mac, Linux, Windows

**Integration Testing:**
- [ ] Skills ‚Üí Subagent delegation works
- [ ] Commands ‚Üí Subagent delegation works
- [ ] Web browser ‚Üí CLI ‚Üí Plugin flow
- [ ] Enhancement ‚Üí Save ‚Üí Reuse workflow
- [ ] Multi-prompt workflows (chaining)

